  "texts": [
    "The majority of existing datasets for text summarization originate from news articles, characterized by a distinct writing style.",
    "To address the scarcity of text in alternative genres and styles, the Wik-iHow dataset has been introduced.",
    "Comprising over 230K pairs of articles and summaries, the dataset is sourced from a diverse range of authors contributing to an online knowledge repository.",
    "• WikiLingua (Ladhak et al, 2020).",
    "The WikiLingua dataset serves the purpose of assessing cross-lingual abstract summarization tasks."
